name: Square linen make up bag - black star
description:
Want something special for your make up or jewellery?

These little bags have been made from 100% natural linen with various patterns screen printed by hand. No two bags are the same.

Lined with coordinating cotton fabric (to match the painted design) and finished with a hand strung pull of wooden beads on leather (nb: as it's leather, don't pull hard as it doesn't have the strength of vinyl. I prefer to pull with the zip head.)

name: Cloth carry all
description:
This is a gorgeous carry all made with Australian designer "Cloth" printed fabric - teal on natural linen.

The bag has a flat base insert, and a double pocket for phones and keys. Use it for your crafty projects or heading out for coffee.

name: NEW! Curlypops Heart Flower Brooch
description:
NEW! CURLYPOPS HEXIE FLOWER BROOCH
$22.50

name: You Are Cool card
description:
Tell someone how you feel without speaking.
An awesome accompaniment to a custom You Are picture or just because you like sending snail mail.
10 x 14cm matte stock. 200gsm.

https://www.etsy.com/au/shop/youareashop

name: NEW! By Nomuu...Deer Girl Art Print - Green Coat with yellow scarf
description:
This a children's decor art print of "Deer Girl Art Print - Green Coat with yellow scarf", perfect as children's decor.

****Note: Photo frame NOT included****

Created with ink pen and digitally coloured (220 gsm / acid free/ c grain) which is a thicker stock with a slight texture to it, using Epson DuraBrite Ultra archival inks. Please note colour will slightly vary from screen to print.

This fits an 8x10 photo frame with a some negative space.

The paper is A4 (21x29.7cm) the actual design is roughly 5.6x8.2" (14.39x20.9 cm) , allowing for a border for easy framing.

Print comes in bend proof envelope and print is dated and signed at the back.

Generously donated by Simone Downey of Nomuu.

See lots more here:

http://shop.nomuu.com/

https://www.etsy.com/au/shop/honeycup

https://www.facebook.com/nomuu

name: Make up purse - around the world
description:
When I was 7, we went to Disney World. I distinctly remember my Dad sitting through no less than 12 trips through "It's A Small World" to satisfy my adoration of the little people of the world. 

This cotton linen print took me right back there (so no, this purse is not just for the kids). Backed with red leather (the faux type, I'm not into the real thing). Lined with 100% cotton blue dot and finished with a leather tassle (Ok, so I'm a little bit into the real thing).

name: NEW! Curlypops Hexie Flower Brooch
description:
Add a bit of colour to your outfit with a gorgeous Hexie Brooch.

This is an original CurlyPops design cut from beautiful Tassie Blackwood, with an insert of her pop flower illustration. (See third picture for actual brooch).

Medium Brooch is approximately 4cm x 3.5cm in size.

Ms Curlypops has generously donated some of her gorgeous jewels to GALB, please go and have a look at her store for many other fabulous finds. 

http://curlypops.bigcartel.com

name: Gift voucher (multiple denominations)
description:
So, you love the idea of Give A Little Bit but can't decide what to buy. Or maybe, the stuff isn't for you but you know someone who'd love it?

Well, a gift voucher is your perfect choice! I'll wrap these up beautifully and enclose a custom card, or send it to you for all that fiddling. Your choice. 

FREE POSTAGE.

name: Cloud cushion (3)
description:
I love clouds.

I associate them with escapism. Whether it's lying on the grass on a sunny day and looking up into scattered white clouds or flying on a plane and peering out the window to a seemingly never ending stream of cotton wool buds, they make me feel calm and relaxed.

So why not bring a bit of that feeling into your home. Sold in sets of two, these mini cloud cushions are perfect for a little chair, bedside table or, in my case, propped up against the computer.

name: Crochet hair clips white -more colours
description:
Handcrafted from start to finish, these crochet clips have been very generously donated by Karen Bayly. Karen herself is a stroke survivor - having suffered a stroke at 44. Despite not having any sensation in her left hand, she's learned to crochet again and donated over 70 of these gorgeous clips.

All handmade, including the pom poms, and stitched for a secure finish (no hot glue gun here!).

Wrapped for giving and posted for $2.

name: Makeup purse - black sheep
description:
Well this purse isn't the black sheep of the family. Possibly some of my most favourite fabric to date, enjoy this 100% linen print with chooks and black sheep in deep earthy tones with neon. The back is a bright pink leather (faux of course, I'm not in to the real thing.)

Lined with 100% cotton in peachy pink dot, and finished with a neon pink silk thread tassle.

name: Restyled army messenger bag (black)
description:
Woah. Here's a blast from the past. The 1980s to be precise. 

My friends and I all had these for school (I sported a denim blue one) with badges, iron on motifs and key chains a dangling. 

For me, these have never gone out of vogue, so I purchased a few (new) and have added thick lining (hand finished); custom made colour coordinating badges and an ornate key ring with five hand made hanging tassels including Danish wooden beads, macrame and resin loops. 

This one's tassel includes Danish wooden beads, macrame and resin. The badges are pale blue smiley, black peace and GALB logo. The lining is sensational - really heavy weight burst cotton in magnificent colours to co-orindate with the badges and tassels. You shouldn't have favourittes but I do and this is it. 

Keep an eye out for more colours and sizes on their way.

name: Sparkling apple mini carry all
description: Coming soon

name: NEW! By Nomuu...Owl and Bunny Illustration -(Woodlands Forest)- Milke in The Woods
description:
Milke is a little bunny rabbit who likes to take adventures into the woods. Milke loves to climb the trees and talk to Mr Owl. Mr Owl helps guide Milke on his adventures.

Created with ink pen and digitally coloured (220 gsm / acid free/ c grain) using Epson DuraBrite Ultra archival inks. Please note colour will slightly vary from screen to print.

The paper has a slight grain to it and it is a heavier stock. Closer to normal greeting card thickness, slightly lighter.

The paper is A4 (21x29.7cm) the actual design is roughly 6.1x7.48" (15.5x19cm), allowing for a border for easy framing. It easily fits into an 8 x 10 frame.

Print comes in bend proof envelope and print is dated and signed at the back. 

Generously donated by Simone Downey of Nomuu.

See lots more here:

http://shop.nomuu.com/

https://www.etsy.com/au/shop/honeycup

https://www.facebook.com/nomuu

name: Baby set - balloons (Pre order now)
description:
I couldn't resist this fabric when I saw it. It's part of the rabbit's range (currently out of stock). Free falling balloons on bright white background. 

The set includes baby pants (to fit up to 12 months) and a 100% cotton long sleeve tee with applique balloons.

name: Lumberjack cafe (Melbourne) $20 Gift Voucher
description:
Lumberjack, formerly known as Flaunt, is a coffee shop · café · food shop located at 484 Bridge Road, Richmond, Victoria 3121.

Fabulous coffee, freshly made delicious food with local produce and a warm homely atmosphere, if you haven't tried Lumberjack yet, you should.

Owner Irene has generously donated these $20 vouchers to help GALB in its mission. 

(03) 9429 5255
	
Mon - Fri: 07:30 - 16:00
Sat - Sun: 08:00 - 16:00

name: Double wrap skull bracelet
description:
Well it's not just Halloween that brings out the vampire, skull loving fiends. 

Double wrap black Howlite beads with interspaced rose gold plated miniature skull (super cute) and Swarovski crystal rose gold rondelle. Finished with nickel free magnetic clasps, this will wrap twice round an adults / child's wrist and for a little little person you'd get it round three times or a loose twice.

name: Fat quarter bag - black butterflies
description:
Pat Manuel has designed and made these gorgeous fully lined handbags. Drawstring tops and little triangular side flaps show a sneak peak of the coordinated yet bright linings. 

100% cotton. 

You'll see each bag has a different trim - tassel, bead (wooden or glass). 

Perfect for shopping, or going out at night with enough room for a small purse, phone and make up.

name: Makeup purse - navy spot
description:
Now I love leather, I'll admit it. And I own leather. But I'm not keen on the idea of sewing with leather. Not that I'm a real animal activist, but it just feels wrong.

So I have designed some gorgeous linen and faux leather purses as a compromise. Thick weight 100% linen on the front side with faux leather (either smooth or snake skin) on the back. Finished with beaded zipper pull from Danish wooden beads. Lined per photograph in either coordinating 100% cotton or waterproof fabric.

This one has waterproof lining and pink colonial knots embroidered on the front to coordinate with pink vinyl backing.

name: Fabric bunting
description:
Stretching out to three metres, this double sided (read, fully reversible) retro bunting is the perfect accessory for your child's room, a play room and every single party you can imagine. 

Available in 5 different colour ways, this is the most environmentally friendly way to decorate, using it time and time again. Not to mention, it's plain gorgeous!

Each design has alternate pattern with plain backing - from front or back it looks the same (see bottom picture). 

Colours from left to right are:

(1) Peace with aqua dot back
(2) Purple paisley with purple dot back
(3) Lime and grey swirl with lime dot back
(4) Mulberry discs with mulberry dot back
(5) Hot pink and green paisley with hot pink dot back 

All back colours shown in third photo.

name: Kids linen bag - boy
description:
These bags were inspired by the sweet hand painted wooden buttons. About a year in the design phase, they feature an appliqué of the button on the front of a natural linen messenger bag, lined with coordinating 100% cotton. Straps are 100% natural cotton webbing.

To avoid frustration with little fumbly fingers, the button is fastened permanently on the flap and the bag closes with a hidden press stud.

description:

Three styles, using denim or natural linen.

Nb: modelled style with stripes/star sold out.
